Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{I won't be all right...}Cháu không ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Chú xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was a shock, that I had been\Ndeceived for so long.}Nó thật là sốc. Cháu đã bị lừa dối quá lâu.
