Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I choose to trust you, the person I know.}chọn tin vào chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
